This is my first Hypernetwork, i use everything as default so, there is no that much of a technical notes other than puting the images to train.

How to use:

I messed around with the prompts and it is quite versatile. I think you should be fine with everything you throw at it: alternate costumes, SFW/NSFW, Loras/Lohas, models, etc.

If you want basic promtps to begin playing around with it, this are the parameters.

Weights: 0.6 - 1.1
